{"PageNumber":22,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":817,"Width":1089,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"title","Text":"#  Disadvantages of Iterative Waterfall Model","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":27,"Y":63},"LeftTop":{"X":27,"Y":23},"RightBottom":{"X":716,"Y":63},"RightTop":{"X":716,"Y":23}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"title","Text":"##  Difficult to Incorporate Change Requests","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":94,"Y":181},"LeftTop":{"X":94,"Y":150},"RightBottom":{"X":639,"Y":181},"RightTop":{"X":639,"Y":150}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"The major drawback of the iterative waterfall model is that all the requirements must be clearly stated before starting the development phase. Customers may change requirements after some time but the iterative waterfall model does not leave any scope to incorporate change requests that are made after the development phase starts.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":94,"Y":435},"LeftTop":{"X":94,"Y":195},"RightBottom":{"X":972,"Y":435},"RightTop":{"X":972,"Y":195}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"title","Text":"##  Incremental Delivery Not Supported","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":94,"Y":505},"LeftTop":{"X":94,"Y":474},"RightBottom":{"X":578,"Y":505},"RightTop":{"X":578,"Y":474}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"In the iterative waterfall model, the full software is completely developed and tested before delivery to the customer. There is no scope for any intermediate delivery. So, customers have to wait a long for getting the software.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":94,"Y":674},"LeftTop":{"X":94,"Y":518},"RightBottom":{"X":976,"Y":674},"RightTop":{"X":976,"Y":518}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":5,"Type":"footer","Text":"14","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":1043,"Y":787},"LeftTop":{"X":1043,"Y":768},"RightBottom":{"X":1064,"Y":787},"RightTop":{"X":1064,"Y":768}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}]}